[
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 0.28,
    "duration": 16.97
  },
  {
    "text": "Introducing the Kawasaki Coro, a",
    "start": 20.48,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "groundbreaking fusion of robotics and",
    "start": 23.039,
    "duration": 3.921
  },
  {
    "text": "motorcycle engineering designed to",
    "start": 24.88,
    "duration": 4.799
  },
  {
    "text": "revolutionize off-road mobility with its",
    "start": 26.96,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Four robotic legs equipped with adaptive",
    "start": 29.679,
    "duration": 4.241
  },
  {
    "text": "hooves, it mimics natural walking",
    "start": 31.76,
    "duration": 4.319
  },
  {
    "text": "movements and effortlessly tackles",
    "start": 33.92,
    "duration": 4.799
  },
  {
    "text": "rugged terrains from grass to gravel.",
    "start": 36.079,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Powered by a 150cc hydrogen engine, the",
    "start": 38.719,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Corio combines eco-friendly innovation",
    "start": 42.239,
    "duration": 4.881
  },
  {
    "text": "with robust performance, demonstrating",
    "start": 44.719,
    "duration": 4.281
  },
  {
    "text": "the future potential of sustainable",
    "start": 47.12,
    "duration": 4.08
  },
  {
    "text": "energy. Riders control it through",
    "start": 49.0,
    "duration": 4.92
  },
  {
    "text": "intuitive horseback inspired movements,",
    "start": 51.2,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "delivering a uniquely immersive",
    "start": 53.92,
    "duration": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": "experience. Debuting at the Osaka Expo",
    "start": 55.68,
    "duration": 7.679
  },
  {
    "text": "2025, Kawasaki's Coro is set to redefine",
    "start": 59.48,
    "duration": 6.92
  },
  {
    "text": "personal mobility, showcasing hydrogen's",
    "start": 63.359,
    "duration": 5.281
  },
  {
    "text": "promise in transforming transportation",
    "start": 66.4,
    "duration": 5.039
  },
  {
    "text": "for a greener",
    "start": 68.64,
    "duration": 2.799
  },
  {
    "text": "tomorrow. The InBall 2 developed by JAXA",
    "start": 73.24,
    "duration": 6.199
  },
  {
    "text": "is a sophisticated free-flying camera",
    "start": 77.2,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "robot engineered to enhance efficiency",
    "start": 79.439,
    "duration": 4.521
  },
  {
    "text": "aboard the International Space Station",
    "start": 81.84,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "ISS. Equipped with advanced navigation",
    "start": 83.96,
    "duration": 5.24
  },
  {
    "text": "software, improved propulsion systems,",
    "start": 86.72,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "and highresolution 4K capable cameras,",
    "start": 89.2,
    "duration": 6.599
  },
  {
    "text": "INTBL 2 autonomously captures photos and",
    "start": 92.72,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "videos, reducing astronauts workload for",
    "start": 95.799,
    "duration": 5.721
  },
  {
    "text": "documentation tasks. It can maneuver",
    "start": 98.88,
    "duration": 4.559
  },
  {
    "text": "precisely within the station's confined",
    "start": 101.52,
    "duration": 4.559
  },
  {
    "text": "spaces, ensuring optimal data collection",
    "start": 103.439,
    "duration": 4.401
  },
  {
    "text": "without human intervention.",
    "start": 106.079,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Additionally, INTBall 2 serves as a",
    "start": 107.84,
    "duration": 4.239
  },
  {
    "text": "platform for technological experiments,",
    "start": 109.759,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "enabling external users to integrate and",
    "start": 112.079,
    "duration": 4.561
  },
  {
    "text": "test new software. This cuttingedge",
    "start": 114.159,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "robotic innovation not only streamlines",
    "start": 116.64,
    "duration": 4.479
  },
  {
    "text": "activities aboard the ISS, but also",
    "start": 118.799,
    "duration": 4.401
  },
  {
    "text": "paves the way for future advancements in",
    "start": 121.119,
    "duration": 6.36
  },
  {
    "text": "space exploration and robotics.",
    "start": 123.2,
    "duration": 4.279
  },
  {
    "text": "Unit's G1 humanoid robot is a",
    "start": 129.84,
    "duration": 5.119
  },
  {
    "text": "groundbreaking innovation in robotics,",
    "start": 132.64,
    "duration": 4.76
  },
  {
    "text": "blending agility, precision, and",
    "start": 134.959,
    "duration": 6.081
  },
  {
    "text": "versatility. Standing at 1.32 m tall,",
    "start": 137.4,
    "duration": 8.12
  },
  {
    "text": "and weighing 35 kg, the G1 features 23°",
    "start": 141.04,
    "duration": 6.8
  },
  {
    "text": "of freedom, enabling dynamic movements",
    "start": 145.52,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "like walking, running, and even",
    "start": 147.84,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "performing acrobatics such as side",
    "start": 150.16,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "flips. Equipped with advanced sensors,",
    "start": 151.84,
    "duration": 5.44
  },
  {
    "text": "including three DLI, DAR, and depth",
    "start": 154.56,
    "duration": 5.92
  },
  {
    "text": "cameras, it achieves 360 zero degree",
    "start": 157.28,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "environmental awareness, making it",
    "start": 160.48,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "suitable for tasks in research,",
    "start": 162.48,
    "duration": 4.52
  },
  {
    "text": "industry, and potentially hazardous",
    "start": 164.48,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "environments. Its three-fingered",
    "start": 167.0,
    "duration": 4.959
  },
  {
    "text": "dextrous hands allow for precise object",
    "start": 169.04,
    "duration": 5.919
  },
  {
    "text": "manipulation, while its 9,000 MIA",
    "start": 171.959,
    "duration": 5.321
  },
  {
    "text": "battery ensures up to 2 hours of",
    "start": 174.959,
    "duration": 5.241
  },
  {
    "text": "operation. With a starting price of",
    "start": 177.28,
    "duration": 5.599
  },
  {
    "text": "$16,000, the G1 is positioned as an",
    "start": 180.2,
    "duration": 4.84
  },
  {
    "text": "accessible platform for robotics",
    "start": 182.879,
    "duration": 4.561
  },
  {
    "text": "research and development, showcasing the",
    "start": 185.04,
    "duration": 6.36
  },
  {
    "text": "future of humanoid robotics.",
    "start": 187.44,
    "duration": 3.96
  },
  {
    "text": "The Dive XL developed by Andural",
    "start": 194.0,
    "duration": 4.879
  },
  {
    "text": "Industries is an extra-large autonomous",
    "start": 196.319,
    "duration": 6.401
  },
  {
    "text": "underwater vehicle XL AUV designed for",
    "start": 198.879,
    "duration": 6.401
  },
  {
    "text": "long range and longduration missions",
    "start": 202.72,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "with a modular and open systems",
    "start": 205.28,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "architecture. It can carry multiple",
    "start": 207.12,
    "duration": 4.24
  },
  {
    "text": "payloads, including large and complex",
    "start": 209.28,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "ones, making it highly adaptable for",
    "start": 211.36,
    "duration": 5.799
  },
  {
    "text": "tasks like seabed surveys, intelligence,",
    "start": 213.84,
    "duration": 6.399
  },
  {
    "text": "surveillance, reconnaissance, ISR, and",
    "start": 217.159,
    "duration": 5.561
  },
  {
    "text": "even strike missions. Powered by an",
    "start": 220.239,
    "duration": 5.121
  },
  {
    "text": "all-electric drivetrain, it can operate",
    "start": 222.72,
    "duration": 4.84
  },
  {
    "text": "underwater for extended periods without",
    "start": 225.36,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "surfacing, enhancing its stealth and",
    "start": 227.56,
    "duration": 5.16
  },
  {
    "text": "operational flexibility. Its compact",
    "start": 229.92,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "design allows for easy transportation",
    "start": 232.72,
    "duration": 4.879
  },
  {
    "text": "and deployment from various platforms,",
    "start": 235.12,
    "duration": 5.6
  },
  {
    "text": "including ships and peers. Dive XL is",
    "start": 237.599,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "setting new standards in maritime",
    "start": 240.72,
    "duration": 4.079
  },
  {
    "text": "autonomy, offering unmatched versatility",
    "start": 242.239,
    "duration": 4.481
  },
  {
    "text": "and endurance for both defense and",
    "start": 244.799,
    "duration": 4.321
  },
  {
    "text": "commercial",
    "start": 246.72,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "applications. Lab grown meat. The lab",
    "start": 251.4,
    "duration": 4.6
  },
  {
    "text": "grown meat, also called cultivated or",
    "start": 253.92,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "cultured meat, is changing everything we",
    "start": 256.0,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "know about how meat is produced. Instead",
    "start": 258.56,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "of raising and slaughtering animals,",
    "start": 260.72,
    "duration": 3.919
  },
  {
    "text": "this process involves collecting animal",
    "start": 262.72,
    "duration": 3.759
  },
  {
    "text": "cells and nurturing them in a",
    "start": 264.639,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "nutrient-rich controlled environment",
    "start": 266.479,
    "duration": 4.561
  },
  {
    "text": "until they grow into real meat. No",
    "start": 268.639,
    "duration": 5.441
  },
  {
    "text": "cruelty, no compromise. The benefits are",
    "start": 271.04,
    "duration": 5.68
  },
  {
    "text": "huge. Dramatically lower greenhouse gas",
    "start": 274.08,
    "duration": 5.44
  },
  {
    "text": "emissions, reduce land and water usage,",
    "start": 276.72,
    "duration": 5.199
  },
  {
    "text": "and the ability to meet global protein",
    "start": 279.52,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "demands more sustainably. It offers the",
    "start": 281.919,
    "duration": 5.361
  },
  {
    "text": "same taste, texture, and nutritional",
    "start": 284.56,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "value as traditional meat, but with a",
    "start": 287.28,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "fraction of the environmental footprint.",
    "start": 289.84,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Major food companies and governments",
    "start": 292.4,
    "duration": 3.76
  },
  {
    "text": "around the world are racing to scale up",
    "start": 294.16,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "this technology. And soon, lab grown",
    "start": 296.16,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "meat might be a regular item in your",
    "start": 298.88,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "grocery store or even your favorite",
    "start": 300.72,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": "restaurant. It's not science fiction.",
    "start": 302.8,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "It's the future of food, and it's",
    "start": 305.52,
    "duration": 5.64
  },
  {
    "text": "happening right now.",
    "start": 307.52,
    "duration": 3.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Clear Space, a Swiss startup, is",
    "start": 314.56,
    "duration": 3.919
  },
  {
    "text": "spearheading efforts to tackle the",
    "start": 316.72,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "escalating problem of space debris. In",
    "start": 318.479,
    "duration": 4.321
  },
  {
    "text": "collaboration with the European Space",
    "start": 321.12,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Agency, ESA, they are developing the",
    "start": 322.8,
    "duration": 5.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Clear Space 1 mission, aiming to be the",
    "start": 325.6,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "first to actively remove debris from",
    "start": 328.32,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Earth's orbit. Initially set to capture",
    "start": 330.24,
    "duration": 5.36
  },
  {
    "text": "the Vega secondary payload adapter Vesa",
    "start": 332.96,
    "duration": 5.519
  },
  {
    "text": "left in orbit since 2013, the mission's",
    "start": 335.6,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "target shifted to the Proba 1 satellite",
    "start": 338.479,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": "due to unforeseen circumstances. Swiss",
    "start": 340.72,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "watch maker Omega has partnered with",
    "start": 343.28,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Clear Space becoming the first private",
    "start": 345.44,
    "duration": 4.319
  },
  {
    "text": "entity to support this groundbreaking",
    "start": 348.0,
    "duration": 3.919
  },
  {
    "text": "initiative. The mission is slated for",
    "start": 349.759,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "launch in the second half of 2026 aboard",
    "start": 351.919,
    "duration": 5.361
  },
  {
    "text": "a Vega C rocket. This collaboration",
    "start": 354.479,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "highlights the increasing role of public",
    "start": 357.28,
    "duration": 3.44
  },
  {
    "text": "private partnerships in ensuring the",
    "start": 359.039,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": "sustainability of space",
    "start": 360.72,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "activities. The Boeing recoverable",
    "start": 366.039,
    "duration": 4.6
  },
  {
    "text": "launch booster was an ambitious concept",
    "start": 368.24,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "developed by Boeing in the 1960s as part",
    "start": 370.639,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": "of the effort to reduce the costs of",
    "start": 373.52,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "launching spacecraft into orbit. The",
    "start": 375.44,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "design featured a double body structure",
    "start": 378.16,
    "duration": 4.159
  },
  {
    "text": "with a specialized booster stage",
    "start": 380.56,
    "duration": 4.24
  },
  {
    "text": "designed to be reused. The concept used",
    "start": 382.319,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "a combination of rocket engines for the",
    "start": 384.8,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "initial ascent and a set of turboan",
    "start": 386.639,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": "engines for the return flight. Once the",
    "start": 388.96,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "spacecraft had been launched into space,",
    "start": 391.44,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "the booster would separate and then",
    "start": 393.36,
    "duration": 4.08
  },
  {
    "text": "engage its turboan engines for a",
    "start": 395.44,
    "duration": 3.84
  },
  {
    "text": "controlled return to Earth where it",
    "start": 397.44,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "would land on a runway for refurbishment",
    "start": 399.28,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": "and reuse. This concept, while",
    "start": 401.44,
    "duration": 5.199
  },
  {
    "text": "promising, was ultimately never built or",
    "start": 404.08,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": "flown as advancements in other space",
    "start": 406.639,
    "duration": 4.161
  },
  {
    "text": "technologies and shifting priorities led",
    "start": 408.88,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "to its cancellation. However, the Boeing",
    "start": 410.8,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "recoverable launch booster helped pave",
    "start": 413.28,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "the way for future reusable rocket",
    "start": 415.52,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "concepts. Kawasaki's Alice system is a",
    "start": 421.96,
    "duration": 5.0
  },
  {
    "text": "groundbreaking step toward the future of",
    "start": 425.039,
    "duration": 4.481
  },
  {
    "text": "smart mobility. Designed to debut at the",
    "start": 426.96,
    "duration": 6.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Osaka Canai Expo in 2025, Alice stands",
    "start": 429.52,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "for accessible linkages for innovative",
    "start": 433.36,
    "duration": 4.559
  },
  {
    "text": "and comfortable experiences. And it's",
    "start": 435.68,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "all about seamless travel. Imagine",
    "start": 437.919,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "stepping into a sleek, compact Alice",
    "start": 440.72,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "cabin that carries you through city",
    "start": 443.039,
    "duration": 5.041
  },
  {
    "text": "streets, then docks into a train, boards",
    "start": 445.12,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "a ferry, or even attaches to a plane",
    "start": 448.08,
    "duration": 5.92
  },
  {
    "text": "without you ever leaving your seat. Each",
    "start": 451.28,
    "duration": 5.199
  },
  {
    "text": "cabin seats up to four people and is",
    "start": 454.0,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "powered by hydrogen fuel, making it",
    "start": 456.479,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": "clean, green, and futuristic. At the",
    "start": 458.88,
    "duration": 7.039
  },
  {
    "text": "heart of it is Kawasaki's innovative OCU",
    "start": 462.319,
    "duration": 6.241
  },
  {
    "text": "VoID power unit born from their",
    "start": 465.919,
    "duration": 5.761
  },
  {
    "text": "motorcycle engine tech. This isn't just",
    "start": 468.56,
    "duration": 5.52
  },
  {
    "text": "a concept. It's a bold vision for a",
    "start": 471.68,
    "duration": 4.959
  },
  {
    "text": "future where transportation is smooth,",
    "start": 474.08,
    "duration": 7.08
  },
  {
    "text": "sustainable, and fully interconnected.",
    "start": 476.639,
    "duration": 4.521
  },
  {
    "text": "Area Gen 2 is Meta's next generation",
    "start": 484.08,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "smart glasses designed to advance",
    "start": 486.56,
    "duration": 5.079
  },
  {
    "text": "research in AI, machine perception, and",
    "start": 488.72,
    "duration": 4.96
  },
  {
    "text": "robotics. Building on the original",
    "start": 491.639,
    "duration": 4.28
  },
  {
    "text": "project, Arya, these glasses feature",
    "start": 493.68,
    "duration": 5.44
  },
  {
    "text": "upgraded sensors, including RGB cameras,",
    "start": 495.919,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "spatial microphones, eyetracking",
    "start": 499.12,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "sensors, and slam cameras for precise",
    "start": 501.199,
    "duration": 5.201
  },
  {
    "text": "positional awareness. New additions like",
    "start": 503.759,
    "duration": 5.761
  },
  {
    "text": "a heart rate monitoring PPG sensor and a",
    "start": 506.4,
    "duration": 5.639
  },
  {
    "text": "contact microphone enhance usability and",
    "start": 509.52,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "accessibility particularly for blind and",
    "start": 512.039,
    "duration": 5.161
  },
  {
    "text": "low vision individuals with ondevice AI",
    "start": 514.159,
    "duration": 5.32
  },
  {
    "text": "capabilities for speech recognition",
    "start": 517.2,
    "duration": 4.319
  },
  {
    "text": "handtracking and simultaneous",
    "start": 519.479,
    "duration": 5.961
  },
  {
    "text": "localization and mapping slam area Gen 2",
    "start": 521.519,
    "duration": 6.561
  },
  {
    "text": "offers 6 to eight hours of active use",
    "start": 525.44,
    "duration": 5.68
  },
  {
    "text": "and a lightweight foldable design. This",
    "start": 528.08,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "innovative device is a significant step",
    "start": 531.12,
    "duration": 4.719
  },
  {
    "text": "forward in wearable technology, paving",
    "start": 533.36,
    "duration": 4.159
  },
  {
    "text": "the way for future advancements in",
    "start": 535.839,
    "duration": 5.521
  },
  {
    "text": "accessibility and AIdriven",
    "start": 537.519,
    "duration": 3.841
  },
  {
    "text": "applications. The Aeronova airships",
    "start": 543.959,
    "duration": 4.761
  },
  {
    "text": "represent a new era in aeronautics,",
    "start": 546.48,
    "duration": 4.08
  },
  {
    "text": "focusing on innovative designs for",
    "start": 548.72,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "passenger and cargo transportation.",
    "start": 550.56,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "These next generation airships are",
    "start": 552.88,
    "duration": 4.28
  },
  {
    "text": "designed to be environmentally friendly,",
    "start": 554.72,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "cost-effective, and capable of",
    "start": 557.16,
    "duration": 4.44
  },
  {
    "text": "longduration year-round flights.",
    "start": 559.04,
    "duration": 4.239
  },
  {
    "text": "Utilizing advanced materials and",
    "start": 561.6,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "patented technologies, Aeronova airships",
    "start": 563.279,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "feature semi- rigid structures,",
    "start": 565.92,
    "duration": 4.08
  },
  {
    "text": "mechanized mooring systems, and the",
    "start": 567.839,
    "duration": 4.721
  },
  {
    "text": "ability to land on small pads or water.",
    "start": 570.0,
    "duration": 4.959
  },
  {
    "text": "They aim to revolutionize air travel by",
    "start": 572.56,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "offering sustainable solutions for",
    "start": 574.959,
    "duration": 5.361
  },
  {
    "text": "various industries including logistics,",
    "start": 577.12,
    "duration": 6.719
  },
  {
    "text": "tourism, and emergency services. With a",
    "start": 580.32,
    "duration": 6.639
  },
  {
    "text": "strong emphasis on safety, efficiency,",
    "start": 583.839,
    "duration": 5.921
  },
  {
    "text": "and versatility, Aeronova is paving the",
    "start": 586.959,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "way for the future of airship",
    "start": 589.76,
    "duration": 4.759
  },
  {
    "text": "technology.",
    "start": 591.519,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 595.99,
    "duration": 5.13
  },
  {
    "text": "The SUJ1 W51 Mustang 1 is a",
    "start": 597.279,
    "duration": 5.761
  },
  {
    "text": "state-of-the-art ultralight aircraft",
    "start": 601.12,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "inspired by the iconic P-51 Mustang of",
    "start": 603.04,
    "duration": 6.56
  },
  {
    "text": "World War II. This 70% scale replica",
    "start": 606.0,
    "duration": 5.72
  },
  {
    "text": "combines timeless design with modern",
    "start": 609.6,
    "duration": 4.479
  },
  {
    "text": "innovations. Featuring a carbon fiber",
    "start": 611.72,
    "duration": 5.239
  },
  {
    "text": "structure, retractable landing gear, and",
    "start": 614.079,
    "duration": 5.76
  },
  {
    "text": "a Garmin G3X glass cockpit for advanced",
    "start": 616.959,
    "duration": 4.481
  },
  {
    "text": "avionics.",
    "start": 619.839,
    "duration": 5.041
  },
  {
    "text": "Powered by a turbocharged Rotax 916is",
    "start": 621.44,
    "duration": 5.079
  },
  {
    "text": "engine, the",
    "start": 624.88,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "SW51 delivers exceptional performance",
    "start": 626.519,
    "duration": 5.32
  },
  {
    "text": "with a climb rate of over 2,000 ft per",
    "start": 629.519,
    "duration": 4.961
  },
  {
    "text": "minute and a cruising speed of 216",
    "start": 631.839,
    "duration": 5.361
  },
  {
    "text": "knots. With its authentic details,",
    "start": 634.48,
    "duration": 4.96
  },
  {
    "text": "including simulated rivets and a Merlin",
    "start": 637.2,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": "engine sound system, the SW51 blends",
    "start": 639.44,
    "duration": 5.36
  },
  {
    "text": "aviation heritage with cuttingedge",
    "start": 643.04,
    "duration": 4.239
  },
  {
    "text": "technology, offering an exhilarating and",
    "start": 644.8,
    "duration": 6.279
  },
  {
    "text": "unique flying experience.",
    "start": 647.279,
    "duration": 3.8
  },
  {
    "text": "NASA's Mars Sample Return, MSR, mission",
    "start": 653.36,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "in collaboration with the European Space",
    "start": 656.24,
    "duration": 5.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Agency, ESA, aims to bring Martian rock,",
    "start": 658.24,
    "duration": 5.76
  },
  {
    "text": "soil, and atmospheric samples back to",
    "start": 661.76,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Earth for comprehensive analysis. The",
    "start": 664.0,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "mission involves multiple steps. The",
    "start": 666.48,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Perseverance rover collects and caches",
    "start": 668.72,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "samples on Mars. A future lander will",
    "start": 670.8,
    "duration": 4.479
  },
  {
    "text": "retrieve these samples and launch them",
    "start": 673.44,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "into Martian orbit. Then an orbiter will",
    "start": 675.279,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": "capture the sample container and return",
    "start": 678.16,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "it to Earth. This complex campaign seeks",
    "start": 680.079,
    "duration": 4.961
  },
  {
    "text": "to provide unprecedented insights into",
    "start": 683.04,
    "duration": 4.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Mars geology and potential signs of past",
    "start": 685.04,
    "duration": 4.96
  },
  {
    "text": "life. However, the mission faces",
    "start": 687.72,
    "duration": 4.679
  },
  {
    "text": "challenges, including escalating costs",
    "start": 690.0,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "estimated at around $10 billion and",
    "start": 692.399,
    "duration": 4.401
  },
  {
    "text": "potential delays pushing the sample",
    "start": 695.04,
    "duration": 4.08
  },
  {
    "text": "return to the late 2030s. To address",
    "start": 696.8,
    "duration": 4.159
  },
  {
    "text": "these issues, NASA is exploring",
    "start": 699.12,
    "duration": 3.44
  },
  {
    "text": "partnerships with private aerospace",
    "start": 700.959,
    "duration": 3.601
  },
  {
    "text": "companies to streamline the mission and",
    "start": 702.56,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "reduce expenses.",
    "start": 704.56,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": "EST Space Mobile is on a mission to",
    "start": 709.64,
    "duration": 5.48
  },
  {
    "text": "revolutionize global communication by",
    "start": 712.64,
    "duration": 4.319
  },
  {
    "text": "creating the world's first space-based",
    "start": 715.12,
    "duration": 4.159
  },
  {
    "text": "cellular broadband network that connects",
    "start": 716.959,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "directly to everyday smartphones. No",
    "start": 719.279,
    "duration": 5.361
  },
  {
    "text": "special hardware needed using advanced",
    "start": 721.839,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": "satellites like Blue Walker 3 with a",
    "start": 724.64,
    "duration": 5.36
  },
  {
    "text": "massive 693 square foot antenna and the",
    "start": 726.639,
    "duration": 5.921
  },
  {
    "text": "upcoming Bluebird satellites. A has",
    "start": 730.0,
    "duration": 4.399
  },
  {
    "text": "already made history with the first ever",
    "start": 732.56,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "space-based voice call and 5G connection",
    "start": 734.399,
    "duration": 5.68
  },
  {
    "text": "from space using an unmodified phone.",
    "start": 737.12,
    "duration": 5.279
  },
  {
    "text": "Partnering with giants like AT&T and",
    "start": 740.079,
    "duration": 4.481
  },
  {
    "text": "Vodafone, the company is working to",
    "start": 742.399,
    "duration": 5.041
  },
  {
    "text": "eliminate connectivity gaps across land,",
    "start": 744.56,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "sea, and air, bringing high-speed 4G and",
    "start": 747.44,
    "duration": 5.519
  },
  {
    "text": "5G coverage to even the most remote",
    "start": 750.56,
    "duration": 4.76
  },
  {
    "text": "corners of the planet. This isn't just",
    "start": 752.959,
    "duration": 4.721
  },
  {
    "text": "innovation. It's a bold step toward",
    "start": 755.32,
    "duration": 6.48
  },
  {
    "text": "truly global mobile connectivity.",
    "start": 757.68,
    "duration": 4.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Smart Swim 2, the nextG augmented",
    "start": 764.079,
    "duration": 4.481
  },
  {
    "text": "reality goggles that are changing the",
    "start": 766.959,
    "duration": 3.761
  },
  {
    "text": "game for swimmers. These high-tech",
    "start": 768.56,
    "duration": 4.36
  },
  {
    "text": "goggles project real-time metrics like",
    "start": 770.72,
    "duration": 5.359
  },
  {
    "text": "distance, time, and heart rate directly",
    "start": 772.92,
    "duration": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": "into your line of sight, so you can",
    "start": 776.079,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "track performance without ever stopping.",
    "start": 778.48,
    "duration": 5.359
  },
  {
    "text": "With a sleeker design, upgraded eye",
    "start": 781.279,
    "duration": 5.041
  },
  {
    "text": "seals for better comfort, and a built-in",
    "start": 783.839,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "heart rate monitor on the strap, they're",
    "start": 786.32,
    "duration": 4.6
  },
  {
    "text": "engineered for peak performance in the",
    "start": 788.959,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "water. Compatible with both iOS and",
    "start": 790.92,
    "duration": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Android, swimmers can sync workouts to",
    "start": 793.839,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": "the Form app and connect with platforms",
    "start": 796.48,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "like Strava. Whether you're training for",
    "start": 798.639,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": "competition or just want smarter swim",
    "start": 801.2,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "sessions, the Smart Swim 2 delivers a",
    "start": 803.44,
    "duration": 7.8
  },
  {
    "text": "powerful boost right before your eyes.",
    "start": 806.24,
    "duration": 5.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Neogamma is an advanced humanoid robot",
    "start": 813.519,
    "duration": 4.481
  },
  {
    "text": "developed by 1X Technologies designed to",
    "start": 815.6,
    "duration": 3.919
  },
  {
    "text": "seamlessly integrate into home",
    "start": 818.0,
    "duration": 2.959
  },
  {
    "text": "environments and assist with daily",
    "start": 819.519,
    "duration": 4.961
  },
  {
    "text": "tasks. With a soft 3D printed nylon knit",
    "start": 820.959,
    "duration": 5.841
  },
  {
    "text": "suit that mimics human movement, Neo",
    "start": 824.48,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Gamma offers enhanced performance,",
    "start": 826.8,
    "duration": 4.96
  },
  {
    "text": "reduce noise, and improved safety with",
    "start": 829.2,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "tendon-driven joint actuation and soft",
    "start": 831.76,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "covers. The robot is powered by advanced",
    "start": 833.76,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "neural networks, allowing it to predict",
    "start": 836.24,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "actions, walk with a human-like gate,",
    "start": 838.48,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "and interact naturally through",
    "start": 841.36,
    "duration": 3.839
  },
  {
    "text": "contextual body language in a customuilt",
    "start": 842.8,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": "language model. Planned for early home",
    "start": 845.199,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "tests in 2025, Neo Gamma could",
    "start": 847.6,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "revolutionize home robotics with an",
    "start": 850.399,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": "estimated price range of 20,000 to",
    "start": 852.72,
    "duration": 5.479
  },
  {
    "text": "$30,000.",
    "start": 855.199,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Autonomous transport pods represent the",
    "start": 861.839,
    "duration": 5.281
  },
  {
    "text": "future of sky-high commuting, offering a",
    "start": 864.24,
    "duration": 5.279
  },
  {
    "text": "sleek, innovative solution to the",
    "start": 867.12,
    "duration": 5.279
  },
  {
    "text": "growing challenges of urban congestion.",
    "start": 869.519,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "These autonomous pods designed to travel",
    "start": 872.399,
    "duration": 4.24
  },
  {
    "text": "above city streets are set to",
    "start": 874.639,
    "duration": 3.721
  },
  {
    "text": "revolutionize how we think about",
    "start": 876.639,
    "duration": 3.841
  },
  {
    "text": "transportation. With their ability to",
    "start": 878.36,
    "duration": 4.44
  },
  {
    "text": "glide along elevated tracks or cable",
    "start": 880.48,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "systems, they bypass traffic and provide",
    "start": 882.8,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "a fast, efficient, and environmentally",
    "start": 885.36,
    "duration": 4.96
  },
  {
    "text": "friendly mode of transport. The system,",
    "start": 887.92,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "like whoosh, is designed to reduce",
    "start": 890.32,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "traffic congestion, lower emissions, and",
    "start": 892.56,
    "duration": 4.719
  },
  {
    "text": "offer a more flexible and affordable",
    "start": 895.44,
    "duration": 4.24
  },
  {
    "text": "commuting option compared to traditional",
    "start": 897.279,
    "duration": 5.201
  },
  {
    "text": "transit. As cities look for smarter ways",
    "start": 899.68,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "to move people, autonomous transport",
    "start": 902.48,
    "duration": 4.52
  },
  {
    "text": "pods could soon become a staple in urban",
    "start": 904.88,
    "duration": 6.399
  },
  {
    "text": "mobility, changing the way we commute",
    "start": 907.0,
    "duration": 4.279
  },
  {
    "text": "forever. The Aki K1 is an AI powered",
    "start": 914.279,
    "duration": 6.36
  },
  {
    "text": "home gym and personal trainer that",
    "start": 918.16,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "brings advanced fitness technology into",
    "start": 920.639,
    "duration": 4.721
  },
  {
    "text": "your living space. It features a compact",
    "start": 922.72,
    "duration": 6.96
  },
  {
    "text": "design folding down to just 0.3 m,",
    "start": 925.36,
    "duration": 6.64
  },
  {
    "text": "making it 90% smaller than traditional",
    "start": 929.68,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "gym equipment. The system offers over",
    "start": 932.0,
    "duration": 5.68
  },
  {
    "text": "140 classes and 280 movements, including",
    "start": 934.72,
    "duration": 5.679
  },
  {
    "text": "strength training, Pilates, yoga, and",
    "start": 937.68,
    "duration": 5.159
  },
  {
    "text": "aerobics, catering to diverse fitness",
    "start": 940.399,
    "duration": 5.521
  },
  {
    "text": "goals. Its AIdriven coaching utilizes",
    "start": 942.839,
    "duration": 5.24
  },
  {
    "text": "motion tracking, and real-time feedback",
    "start": 945.92,
    "duration": 4.479
  },
  {
    "text": "to create personalized workout plans",
    "start": 948.079,
    "duration": 3.921
  },
  {
    "text": "tailored to your fitness level and",
    "start": 950.399,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "objectives. The AEK K1 also provides",
    "start": 952.0,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "comprehensive fitness assessments,",
    "start": 954.959,
    "duration": 4.481
  },
  {
    "text": "monitoring cardiovascular endurance,",
    "start": 957.04,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "muscle strength, flexibility, and more,",
    "start": 959.44,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "ensuring a holistic approach to your",
    "start": 962.16,
    "duration": 5.46
  },
  {
    "text": "health and wellness journey.",
    "start": 963.92,
    "duration": 9.289
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 967.62,
    "duration": 5.589
  }
]